@startuml
title Statechart diagram of the plane lifecycle

[*] --> Order
state Order
state "Arrival" as Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state "Out of Service" as OutOfService
state Historic

Order --> Arrival : plane acquired
Arrival --> Preparation : plane arrived
Preparation --> Operations : plane prepared
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights
Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced
Operations --> OutOfService : plane no longer available
Preparation --> Historic : plane permanently withdrawn
Maintenance --> Historic : plane permanently withdrawn
OutOfService --> [*] : plane restored
Historic --> [*] : plane removed
@enduml
